msgid "New Wiki"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: pregen/source/blog/2015-07-07-coming-soon-new-home-page-and-wiki/index.adoc:92
msgid "And yes, we have a new wiki (called 'docs')."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: pregen/source/blog/2015-07-07-coming-soon-new-home-page-and-wiki/index.adoc:94
