"No more MediaWiki, no more databases. Pages are stored in plain text and may "
"be easily edited in Notepad (although I recommend https://atom.io[Atom], "
"hehe ;-) )."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: pregen/source/blog/2015-07-07-coming-soon-new-home-page-and-wiki/index.adoc:96
msgid ""
"Docs use http://asciidoctor.org[AsciiDoc] for markup now. The preferred "
"image format is https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WebP[WebP] (it's open and has "
"better compression than JPEG and PNG)."
